Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.47,0:01:32.78,Main,Blackbeard,0,0,0,,Darkness will consume you, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.31,0:01:34.71,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:37.28,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'll find One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:42.05,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,and become the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:39.94,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,All pirates who seek One Piece\Nstrive to reach the second half of the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.94,0:02:42.57,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The place called the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:51.31,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, the only one who ever conquered that ocean\Nwas the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:57.78,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The New World has killed\Nthe dreams and ambitions of countless pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.29,0:03:03.49,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,And now, the boy who ate the Gomu Gomu Fruit\Nand became a rubber man,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:07.25,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nare going to challenge that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:11.54,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:18.56,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,In order to defeat one of the Four Emperors, rulers of the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:23.89,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Luffy and his crew formed a Pirate Alliance with\N Trafalgar Law and have invaded Dress Rosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:29.89,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Luffy made it past the first round of a battle tournament, with the Mera Mera fruit as a prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:34.73,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,And now, as the final block begins, the defeated warriors are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:36.67,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:40.07,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,Might you possibly be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:45.37,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,His Highness, King Riku?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:51.33,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,After having fallen so far,\N there really isn't any point in hiding it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:07.76,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Luffy-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:11.40,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Oh, I know you!  You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:14.73,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,N-No wait!  I'm not him!  I'm Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:18.06,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Nevah mind dat...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:19.73,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Ah, it's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:22.83,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Ah'm too nervous to speak properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:24.71,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,If you don't want anything, then I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:26.93,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I want to cheer on Rebecca up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:29.91,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Dun' go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:33.81,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,I-I was asthed by Z-Zoro-senbai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:34.50,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:35.71,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,By Zoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:39.01,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Ya!  He asthed be to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.01,0:04:41.45,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I see.  So where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:44.08,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,H-He'th outside da golosseum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.08,0:04:46.38,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Ah'll show ya da way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.38,0:04:47.60,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Dis way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:50.77,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Right.  I'm counting on you, hen-comb.
